name: v0.0.24
body:
* Prevent company and developer apps from always showing as modify
* Add consumer_secret and consumer_key into developer and company apps.  These are populated from the last element in the credentials list
* If a proxy deployment already exists read it in on create and update
* resolve issues with latest updates on read
* update readme with examples using latest and with new versions config for provider

name: better state management and error handling
body:
* Only remove state on 404s. Much better state handling with this change
* Create, Fail, Update on proxy deployment create if state is not accurate
* Handle, log, and display errors consistently
* Add testing and build instruction in README
* Built on Terraform 0.11.1
